:

1. *Hiljadu* puta sam vam ponovio da se ne igramo vatrom. (I have repeated a thousand times for you not to play with fire.)
2. *Hiljadu* su puta zaista zahtevalo da se uloži veliki trud. (A thousand times really needed to put in a lot of effort.)
3. *Hiljadu* bih puta mogao da govorim o njenoj lepoti. (I could talk a thousand times about her beauty.)
4. *Hiljadu* su puta pokušali da dođu do rešenja, ali bez uspeha. (They tried a thousand times to find a solution, but without success.)